        "page_1": {
            "all_text_blocks": [
                {
                    "bbox": [
                        66.02400207519531,
                        57.403221130371094,
                        307.093994140625,
                        91.04000854492188
                    ],
                    "text": "E N C R A F T  A I   \u00b7   E N G I N E E R I N G  T A K E - H O M E \nMEP Drawing Interpretation"
                },
                {
                    "bbox": [
                        66.02400207519531,
                        93.30318450927734,
                        287.62567138671875,
                        105.07758331298828
                    ],
                    "text": "AI Engineering Intern  \u00b7  Suggested duration: 2 days"
                },
                {
                    "bbox": [
                        66.02400207519531,
                        115.1432113647461,
                        546.345703125,
                        168.67762756347656
                    ],
                    "text": "This exercise reflects a problem we work on directly: the automated interpretation of MEP (mechanical, \nelectrical, and plumbing) construction drawings for enterprise clients. The task below is a deliberately \nnarrow version of it. We are evaluating how you scope, reason, and build, rather than the finish of the \nfinal product."
                },
                {
                    "bbox": [
                        66.02400207519531,
                        182.8400115966797,
                        118.07599639892578,
                        196.2200164794922
                    ],
                    "text": "The task"
                },
                {
                    "bbox": [
                        66.02400207519531,
                        202.02322387695312,
                        546.94775390625,
                        227.7176055908203
                    ],
                    "text": "Build a web application, runnable locally, in which a user uploads an MEP drawing and asks a question \nabout it. The application answers using a vision-language model (VLM)."
                },
                {
                    "bbox": [
                        66.02400207519531,
                        236.85317993164062,
                        260.98565673828125,
                        248.62757873535156
                    ],
                    "text": "Two requirements apply to every answer:"
                },
                {
                    "bbox": [
                        77.06400299072266,
                        254.25320434570312,
                        524.959716796875,
                        266.027587890625
                    ],
                    "text": "\u2013 Grounding. The answer must show where on the drawing the information was found, with an"
                },
                {
                    "bbox": [
                        89.06400299072266,
                        267.6932067871094,
                        204.7056884765625,
                        279.46759033203125
                    ],
                    "text": "indication of confidence."
                },
                {
                    "bbox": [
                        77.06400299072266,
                        285.6932067871094,
                        532.6829223632812,
                        297.46759033203125
                    ],
                    "text": "\u2013 Uncertainty. Where the system is not confident, it should flag the item for human review rather"
                },
                {
                    "bbox": [
                        89.06400299072266,
                        299.1332092285156,
                        146.23568725585938,
                        310.9075927734375
                    ],
                    "text": "than guess."
                },
                {
                    "bbox": [
                        66.02400207519531,
                        324.83001708984375,
                        152.75599670410156,
                        338.2099914550781
                    ],
                    "text": "Your drawings"
                },
                {
                    "bbox": [
                        73.10399627685547,
                        347.61322021484375,
                        236.0256805419922,
                        359.3876037597656
                    ],
                    "text": "Drawing \nSource & what it is"
                },
                {
                    "bbox": [
                        73.10399627685547,
                        368.4931945800781,
                        126.31584167480469,
                        392.3876037597656
                    ],
                    "text": "Drawing 1 \n(primary)"
                },
                {
                    "bbox": [
                        148.10000610351562,
                        368.61322021484375,
                        537.0828247070312,
                        405.34759521484375
                    ],
                    "text": "RXR Welcome Center \u2014 HVAC Floor Plan (M-101) \nA single HVAC floor plan with numerous ceiling diffusers and a symbol legend. The Drawing \n1 questions below apply to this sheet."
                },
                {
                    "bbox": [
                        73.10399627685547,
                        414.59320068359375,
                        535.9357299804688,
                        462.3675842285156
                    ],
                    "text": "Drawing 2 \nMuswellbrook Depot \u2014 Mechanical Services \nA separate mechanical set from a different source \u2014 a cover sheet with legends and floor-\nplan layouts. The Drawing 2 questions test whether your application generalises beyond the \nfirst sheet."
                },
                {
                    "bbox": [
                        66.02400207519531,
                        479.1700134277344,
                        323.5660095214844,
                        492.54998779296875
                    ],
                    "text": "The questions your application must answer"
                },
                {
                    "bbox": [
                        66.02400207519531,
                        498.35321044921875,
                        540.738525390625,
                        551.767578125
                    ],
                    "text": "Your application should answer all ten questions below, and the same application must work on both \ndrawings without logic hard-coded to a single file. Every answer should indicate where on the drawing \nthe information was found and flag anything uncertain. Where the correct answer is that an item is not \npresent, the system should report that rather than return something that is not there."
                },
                {
                    "bbox": [
                        66.02400207519531,
                        560.5587768554688,
                        311.0256652832031,
                        572.868408203125
                    ],
                    "text": "Drawing 1 \u2014 RXR Welcome Center HVAC plan"
                },
                {
                    "bbox": [
                        74.06400299072266,
                        577.1032104492188,
                        512.795654296875,
                        588.8776245117188
                    ],
                    "text": "1. How many ceiling supply diffusers are shown on this floor, and where is each one located?"
                },
                {
                    "bbox": [
                        74.06400299072266,
                        595.5831909179688,
                        527.9876098632812,
                        607.3576049804688
                    ],
                    "text": "2. What return-air and transfer grilles are shown, and how are they distinguished from the supply"
                },
                {
                    "bbox": [
                        89.06400299072266,
                        609.023193359375,
                        137.47567749023438,
                        620.797607421875
                    ],
                    "text": "diffusers?"
                },
                {
                    "bbox": [
                        74.06400299072266,
                        627.503173828125,
                        400.9256591796875,
                        639.277587890625
                    ],
                    "text": "3. List the exhaust fans on the sheet and their approximate locations."
                },
                {
                    "bbox": [
                        74.06400299072266,
                        645.983154296875,
                        527.6101684570312,
                        657.757568359375
                    ],
                    "text": "4. What general notes apply to the diffusers and ductwork on this sheet \u2014 for example, anything"
                },
                {
                    "bbox": [
                        89.06400299072266,
                        659.5431518554688,
                        282.3456726074219,
                        671.3175659179688
                    ],
                    "text": "specified for all diffusers or all duct runs?"
                },
                {
                    "bbox": [
                        74.06400299072266,
                        678.023193359375,
                        520.5775756835938,
                        689.797607421875
                    ],
                    "text": "5. Does the sheet contain any flag notes or keynotes indicating an unresolved field condition or"
                },
                {
                    "bbox": [
                        89.06400299072266,
                        691.4591674804688,
                        338.88568115234375,
                        703.2335815429688
                    ],
                    "text": "coordination conflict to verify? If so, summarise each."
                },
                {
                    "bbox": [
                        66.02400207519531,
                        711.5447998046875,
                        322.6656799316406,
                        723.8544311523438
                    ],
                    "text": "Drawing 2 \u2014 Muswellbrook Mechanical Services"
                }
            ],
